title: WebQoof: No, Kejriwal Did Not Visit Imran Khan to Congratulate Him
subtitle: Soon after Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaaf (PTI) chairman Imran Khan emerged victorious in the general elections held recently, a post that claimed Delhi Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal visited Islamabad to congratulate him.
author: www.thequint.com
vclaim:
But as pointed by SMHoaxSlayer, this photo is actually from two years ago when Khan was visiting India.

In March 2016, Khan met Kejriwal at his Delhi residence. It was actually Pakistan’s now PM-in-waiting who presented the Delhi chief minister with a bouquet.
